data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence, a perfect choice for first-time homebuyers or savvy investors. Situated in a tranquil setting on a quiet dead-end street, this property offers a combination of comfort and convenience that is hard to beat.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the spacious front room, adorned with real hardwood floors that exude warmth and character. The focal point of this room is a cozy fireplace, ideal for those chilly winter evenings. This inviting space seamlessly flows into the open kitchen floor plan, providing a perfect setting for entertaining friends and family.  One standout feature of this home is the separate laundry room, offering both convenience and extra storage space. Additionally, it provides easy access to the mechanical systems, including a newer hot water heater, ensuring your household runs smoothly.  The three well-proportioned bedrooms are cleverly laid out, providing ample room for relaxation and personalization. The full bathroom is thoughtfully designed and easily accessible from all bedrooms, enhancing daily convenience.  Step outside into the large fenced-in backyard, a blank canvas for your landscaping dreams. With its generous size, this space presents exciting possibilities for future expansion, whether you envision a lush garden, outdoor entertainment area, or a playground for children.  This property's location is a true gem. It's just a short walk or bike ride away from public access to the Gunnison River and the recreational path leading to the Whitewater park. Nature enthusiasts and outdoor lovers will appreciate the easy access to these natural attractions.  With its combination of charm, convenience, and potential, don't miss this opportunity to make this residence your own. Schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities of calling this place home.
